title: Chef Boy Bonez on Making a Career Out of Popping His Eyes Out Of His Head
description:
ChefBoyBonez talks about his come-up, his music, going viral for his eyes poppin out, having an eye condition that causes it, battle rap and more. ----- 00:00 Intro 1:59 Bonez actually battled before 7:40 Caught a case for stealing a sidekick, got on house arrest for 6 months 11:55 Bonez's response to Supreme Patty Windex viral video 13:19 Bonez was self-conscious about his eyes before posting his first video 17:28 Bonez actually has thyroid eyes diseased which makes his eyes pop out 19:44 This took him to AGT and GGT (Germany Got Talent) 24:13 Bonez made more money with eye-popping than actual music, eye-popping pays the bills 28:39 Keeping his content kids friendly for Tikok and for his son 29:16 Girls have a fetish about his eyes on some kinky shit 30:57 Bonez building a thyroid foundation, lost his mom just a few days ago, so he wants to leave something tangible 35:33 Music in the works with Absoul, give Absoul his flowers, he's an amazing talent in the studio ----- NO JUMPER PATREON http://www.patreon.com/nojumper CHECK OUT OUR NEW SPOTIFY PLAYLIST https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5te...
